description: This file is a JavaScript source file serving as an entry point for a React application. It sets up the React DOM rendering by selecting the root DOM node and rendering the main App component within React's StrictMode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering the React component tree into the specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React components into the created root.
